hopobject.body: We used to work together kamagra gel use The only putative advantage of making sweet chemicals a part of our diets is the calories and sugar they take out. If they don't really do that, there is no excuse for them whatsoever. Perhaps they do help with this, but the burden of proof resides with those claiming the benefit, not with those of us who doubt it. If something implies it helps with dieting, there should be evidence of that benefit. Such evidence as exists is murky at best.
